Now, if you ever have had those chocoholic-cravings for that Frozen Coffee special especially for breakfast in the boroughs-- this is always the place to run into -- if the line doesn't keep you from getting to work on-time. Or snakes waay beyond the entry way into the place ! Let's saay that for that nearly half of the 'competitor-next-door's' blonder assets -- munching a couple of cake donuts with frosting with a coffee chaser should hit-the-spot right away till lunchtime. (Naybe?)  But who's counting calories until you need to meet the personal trainer for that "Killer-Workout" later ... ouch !! So, whenever someone gets that hankering for a less than fulfilling food experience that doesn't include The Full Meal Deal or Brunch Menu -- I yake a hint and cheat !  Seriously. Who doesn't like donuts and coffee ?? The airlines won't serve you unless you buy it before you get On-Board. (Honestly, they should be cutting a deal with DD ... like Disney and 21st Century FOX.) But whatever -- right. So, if donuts are more to you than the Griddle -- Go For It  ! ! Surfers like donuts too.
